brand5 (#F25C54) — Strong red clay

Use for primary actions: main buttons, CTAs, highlights.

Example: bg-brand5 hover:bg-brand4 text-white

brand4 (#F27059) — Burnt orange

Use for hover states or secondary buttons.

Keeps contrast but still on-theme.

brand3 (#F4845F) — Coral

Use for accents: icons, links, small highlights.

Example: link hover underline, chart highlights.

brand2 (#F79D65) — Peach

Use for background sections or cards.

Example: bg-brand2 text-gray-800 for a card background.

brand1 (#F7B267) — Soft amber

Use for neutral background fills (headers, footers, subtle highlights).

Example: bg-brand1 text-gray-900 for a navbar.
